text: Estádio Antônio Aquino Lopes also known as Florestão is a football stadium in Rio Branco, Acre, Brazil. The stadium was inaugurated on 2011 with a maximum capacity of 10,000 spectators. ==References== * Category:Football venues in Acre (state) Category:Sports venues in Acre (state) Category:Sports venues completed in 2011 Category:Rio Branco, Acre
